@host = {{host}}
@token = {{token}}

### Listar conductores
GET {{host}}/api/conductores
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear conductor
POST {{host}}/api/conductores
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Carlos",
  "apellido": "Gómez",
  "dni": "30111222",
  "licencia": "L-2025-001",
  "licencia_vencimiento": "2027-12-31"
}

### Obtener conductor por id
GET {{host}}/api/conductores/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Actualizar conductor
PUT {{host}}/api/conductores/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Carlos",
  "apellido": "Gómez",
  "dni": "30111222",
  "licencia": "L-2025-001",
  "licencia_vencimiento": "2028-01-31"
}

### Eliminar conductor
DELETE {{host}}/api/conductores/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
